aven” to our construction to do list now.\r\n\r\nWe left the plot with a new air of satisfied calm - the shed roof was repaired before the rains returned and the shed interior began to take shape as the "Room of One\'s Own Mug" returns to it\'s rightful centre stage spot in the prized construction.', 'A Stormy Kind of Calm', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '300-revision-13', '', '', '2009-11-16 12:30:09', '2009-11-16 11:30:09', '', 300, 'http://www.earthwoman.co.uk/2009/11/16/300-revision-13/', 0, 'revision', '', 0, ''); 
