n\r\nI did give them a cup of tea though.', 'Parental Visitation', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '338-revision-2', '', '', '2009-12-03 16:18:59', '2009-12-03 15:18:59', '', 338, 'http://www.earthwoman.co.uk/2009/12/03/338-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0, ''); 
